                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> you're killing mobs too fast and don't have enough hp gear. if you take your time killing mobs, you will end the fight near full mana, so you won't have to med quite as long. <br /><br />exactly what tanatus said. if you're always in the middle of killing a mob, you won't run out of hp, just keep using the lifetap over time whenever you need to. also, make sure you have enough hp gear so that when you use the tap over time, you take advantage of all of it's healing. <br /><br /></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
                    </tr>
